      <h2>New Volunteers</h2>

      <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12px;">We
      need volunteers of all stripes and abilities to help us fulfill our
      mission and keep quality bikes rolling out of our shop.&nbsp; When
      you give your valuable time and skills to the Bike Depot, you are
      impacting kids and adults and helping to spread biking throughout
      Denver.&nbsp;</span></p>

      <p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:12px;">No
      previous mechanical knowledge is required!&nbsp; We need folks to
      help with marketing, design, website, fundraising, greeting,
      sorting, cleaning, Craigslist posting, data entry, etc.&nbsp; The
      Bike Depot is almost completely staffed by volunteers and it is
      their generous support that keeps us running and getting bikes into
      the hands of those in our community that need them.</span></p>

